<HEAD><TITLE>Equinox International - Advanced Marketing Seminars - Seminar Offerings</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="images/a_bkg4.jpg" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800040" ALINK="#000000">


<MAP NAME="a_bar1">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="404,0,465,114" HREF="index.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="347,0,400,114" HREF="qcform.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="294,1,344,114" HREF="ghindex.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="239,0,290,114" HREF="whatsnew.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="181,0,237,114" HREF="opportun.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="128,1,179,114" HREF="products.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="72,2,125,112" HREF="company.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="0,4,68,111" HREF="#top">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="0,0,466,114" HREF="index.html">
</MAP>
<!--Map by Web Hotspots 2.0  http://www.cris.com/~automata/ -->

<a name="top">
<IMG SRC="images/h_title1.jpg" ALT="Equinox International" WIDTH=483 HEIGHT=108 BORDER=0>

<center>
<font size=+3 color=#800040><STRONG>Advanced Marketing Seminars</STRONG></font><p>
</center>
<CENTER>
<img src="images/ams.gif" ALT="Advanced Marketing Seminars"><BR><IMG SRC="images/p_semin.jpg" ALT="Seminar" WIDTH=202 HEIGHT=136 BORDER=0>
</CENTER><BR>

<STRONG>Basic Building Blocks to Success</STRONG><BR>
This is a two-day introduction to the specific business practices separating very 
successful achievers from average people.  this basic training highlights how to build a 
productive, profitable distribution network.  With an A to Z approach, this program 
covers a vast array of information, including how to develop customers, how to 
demonstrate products, how to present the Equinox opportunity, and how to develop a sales 
force.<P>

<STRONG>Advanced Basic Building Blocks to Success</STRONG><BR>
This advanced basic training offers further details on the subjects 
addressed in Basic Building Blocks and highlights more specific 
aspects of the business. This two day training teaches in greater 
depth how to make effective product and opportunity presentations, 
as well as valuable closing techniques and proven methods for developing 
and motivating a solid, dynamic, high volume sales force.<P>

<STRONG>Millionaire Workshop</STRONG><BR>
This unique, hard-hitting program focuses on the ability to negotiate and achieve our desired results. From closing a retail sale to winning an argument, the Millionaire Workshop reveals the secrets to overcoming virtually any objection! A confrontive program that is not for the weak-hearted, it exposes the hundreds of manipulations we face on a daily basis and addresses the psychology behind it all. The information learned in this workshop allows us to <i>take</i> control instead of <i>being</i> controlled.<P>

<STRONG>Leadership</STRONG><BR>
Specifically designed to help people discover and develop their leadership qualities, this program focuses on how to create and motivate a large sales force and how to develop the closing skills necessary to produce high sales volumes. Leadership teaches the powerful management skills that will keep a growing sales force performing at peak levels. This training also teaches how we can develop and maintain a large, productive group by developing leadership qualities in our sales leaders. The larger our leaders' groups are and the higher their sales volumes, the larger our paychecks become!<P>

<STRONG>Creating a Perpetual Money Machine</STRONG><BR>
This unique program features an exciting lineup of "Hollywood" characters, each of whom personifies and explores a specific aspect of our business. This fun-filled weekend is packed with success laws and principles taught by the entertaining characters who share their solutions to life's problems and business challenges through analogies and clever examples. Heralded by many as the most valuable and comprehensive learning experience of a lifetime, this program is a must for every success minded person.<P>

<STRONG>Journey Beyond Perception</STRONG><BR>
This week-long experience unlocks the ability to understand our true talents and abilities. Journey Beyond Perception is a journey into reality, embracing in detail how each of us listens, reasons, arrives at conclusions, and makes decisions. This amazing program gives us an understanding about who we are, how we became who we are, and how easy it is to "rewrite" our old programming in order to achieve the results we desire. This event has produced documented results so powerful that they are considered almost impossible to all but those who have completed the course!<P>

<STRONG>Training Tools</STRONG><BR>
In addition to these cutting-edge training programs, state of the art audio and video training materials are available through both Equinox and Advanced Marketing Seminars. These training seminars, combined with the informative audio and video programs available, create the most complete and comprehensive training and support system in the world. These success tools will inform, motivate, and inspire each of us to be the best we can be–not only in marketing, but in all areas of our lives.<P>

