<center>
<font size=+2><i>Steve Gould<br>President</i></font><br>
<img src="images/stevgoul.jpg" border=0 ALT="Steve Gouldd"><p>
</center>
<blockquote>
  Steve Gould brings many of the leadership qualities and vision to his position as President
  of Equinox that his brother Bill Gouldd does to his role as the company's founder. Steve's
  unwavering focus on hard work and bottom-line results made him successful as a field
  representative, sales trainer, and consultant for several major marketing organizations
  before he joined his brother's quest to build the finest marketing company in history.
  Rising through the ranks of Equinox, Steve gained valuable hands-on experience in the
  development of all the departments now existing within the Equinox corporate structure.
  His many years of experience in the direct sales industry have resulted in a thorough
  understanding of the responsibilities of the home office to the field. Steve's wide range of
  experience and excellent management skills combined with a remarkable ability to create
  revolutionary concepts and programs impacting the entire direct sales industry have
  contributed greatly to the company's amazing growth. His understanding of cost and
  quality control, organizational development, and productivity ensures a company
  infrastructure and corporate culture guaranteed to achieve excellence, offering numerous
  benefits to the people whose lives it touches. <p>
</blockquote>

