<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Equinox International-Products</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="images/a_bkg4.jpg" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800040" ALINK="#000000">

<MAP NAME="a_bar1">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="404,0,465,114" HREF="index.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="347,0,400,114" HREF="qcform.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="294,1,344,114" HREF="ghindex.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="239,0,290,114" HREF="whatsnew.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="181,0,237,114" HREF="opportun.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="128,1,179,114" HREF="products.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="72,2,125,112" HREF="company.html">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="0,4,68,111" HREF="#top">
<AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="0,0,466,114" HREF="index.html">
</MAP>
<!--Map by Web Hotspots 2.0  http://www.cris.com/~automata/ -->

<a name="top">
<IMG SRC="images/h_title1.jpg" ALT="Equinox International" WIDTH=483 HEIGHT=108 BORDER=0>




<center>
<font size=+2 color=#005300>Rain Forest Resources</font><BR>
<i><font size=+2 color=#C507B7>Botanical Skin Care Products</i></font><p>
</center>




<CENTER><IMG SRC="images/p11_4.jpg" ALT="Rain Forest Skin Care" WIDTH=288 HEIGHT=158 BORDER=0></CENTER><BR CLEAR=BOTH>
<font size=+1>Clarifying Facial Cleanser</font><br>
This unique tropical blend contains various botanicals that have been identified as having properties beneficial to the skin since the 18th century. Hawaiian White Ginger Root Extract and Jaboncillo Extract are used for their superior cleansing ability, and the emollients Bladderwack and Matricaria Extracts are included for their skin soothing abilities. This excellent cleanser produces a rich lather, opens the pores for deep cleaning, and leaves the skin feeling refreshed.<p>

<font size=+1>Purifying Toning Mist</font><br>
A light spray on the face after cleansing induces the refreshing feeling of the tropics thanks to a unique combination of ten herbs and flowers. Its superior moisturizing properties leave the skin with a wonderfully luxurious feel. For best results, follow with either a daytime or nighttime moisturizer.<p>

<font size=+1>Botanical Facial Scrub</font><br>
A combination of rain forest botanicals and very fine pumice creates a superior cleansing and moisturizing formula. 
Macadamia Nut and Brazil Nut Oils are included to help keep the skin smooth, soft, and healthy looking. 
This is an excellent exfoliation treatment.<p>

<font size=+1>Purifying Clay Masque</font><br>
Fresh Water Silt-a coarse grained clay, is specially blended with rain forest botanicals, such as Allspice Extract, Cohune Oil, and Brazil Nut Oil. This deep cleaning treatment is ideal for skin that has been stressed by environmental conditions. It leaves the skin feeling invigorated and naturally refreshed.<p>

<font size=+1>Daytime Moisturizer With Retinyl A</font><br> 
Some of the richest ingredients found in the rain forest have been combined with Retinyl A Palmitate, a product shown in studies to thicken the epidermis and dermis, increase skin elasticity, and normalize dry, parched skin. Natural extracts such as Matricaria, Calendula, and Yarrow help keep skin looking youthful and healthy. This superb moisturizer is an excellent foundation for makeup and is gentle enough to use every day.<p>

<font size=+1>Night Treatment With Alpha Hydroxy</font><br> 
Five Alpha Hydroxy Acids--Lactic Acid, Sugar Cane Extract, Citrus Extract, Apple Extract, and Green Tea Extract--are included in this outstanding  skin treatment to gently exfoliate the skin. Cohune Oil is included for its superior moisturizing qualities. Used nightly, it gently helps to renew and protect the skin, while keeping it soft, smooth, and supple.<p>

<font size=+1>Botanical Eye Gel</font><br>
Our naturally rich, glycol-free formula is designed to help protect the very delicate tissue surrounding the eye. This special gel contains Aloe Vera, renowned for its healing properties, and Jaboncillo Extract, which produces a protective film that may help prevent fine lines caused by dryness resulting from exposure to the elements. Extracts of Cucumber, Comfrey, and Witch Hazel make it safe to use every day.<p>

<font size=+1>Rain Forest Resources Skin Care System</font><br>
Equinox has created a skin care system that is absolutely unequaled. Our combination of the finest cosmetic ingredients available, including Alpha Hydroxy Fruit Acids and Retinyl A Palmitate, with moisturizing rain forest botanicals provides the ultimate in a skin care regime and takes the challenge out of skin care. These exceptional products naturally nourish and moisturize the skin, thereby helping to combat the harsh effects of the environment that can cause the skin to age prematurely. The Rain Forest Resources Skin Care System includes all seven incredible products that were designed to be used together as a complete skin care system.<p>




For more information on how to order products or
to become an independent Equinox representative, please complete our online 
<a href="qcform.html">Inquiry Form</a>.<p>

