<a name="top">
<IMG SRC="images/h_title1.jpg" ALT="Equinox International" WIDTH=483 HEIGHT=108 BORDER=0>




<center>
<font size=+2 color=#005300>Rain Forest Resources</font><BR>
<font size=+2 color=#00B5B5><i>Botanical Body Care Products</i></font><p>
</center>




<CENTER><IMG SRC="images/p12_4.jpg" ALT="Rain Forest Body Care" WIDTH=288 HEIGHT=158 HSPACE=10 VSPACE=10 BORDER=0></CENTER><br clear=both>

<font size=+1>Protective Hand & Body Moisturizer</font><br>
This super-rich moisturizer contains botanicals that were traditionally used by the ancient Mayans for medicinal and ceremonial purposes. The unique combination of Allspice Extract and Aloe Vera Gel produces an exceptional emollient that absorbs completely and leaves the skin feeling silky and smooth.<p>

<font size=+1>Aromatherapy Shower Gel</font><br>
Natural fragrances noted for their relaxing aromatherapy qualities, Aloe Vera Gel, and Jaboncillo Extract are combined to produce an invigorating shower gel with superior cleansing and moisturizing capabilities. This exotic formulation cleans thoroughly and leaves the skin feeling soft and refreshed.<p>

<font size=+1>Botanical Body Scrub</font><br>
A unique blend of plants, fruits, and herbs including crushed Apricot Seeds and Jaboncillo Extract gently cleanses the skin while exfoliating dead skin cells. Mandarin and Orange Oils offer soothing aromatherapy benefits. This incredible scrub invigorates and refreshes as it gives the skin a radiant, healthy glow.<p>

<font size=+1>Exotic Blend Body Oil</font><br>
Exceptional emollients such as Brazil Nut and Macadamia Nut Oils penetrate deeply into the pores to keep the skin soft, smooth, and supple. Allspice Extract bestows the lush scent of a tropical forest. Spray on after a shower or bath to give the body a sensuously luxurious feel.<p>

<font size=+1>Aromatherapy Herbal Bath Foam</font><br>
This combination of tropical herbs is ideal for use after a stressful day. Aloe Vera Gel, Goldenseal Extract, and Hawaiian White Ginger Root Extract moisturize the skin while soothing and relaxing tired, aching muscles. Aromatherapy extracts provide a truly exotic bathing experience.<p>

<font size=+1>Rain Forest Resources Body Care System</font><br>
The five excellent products in our Body Care System were designed to nourish and protect the skin. As the largest organ in the human body, our skin is deserving of extra care and attention. Damage from the sun together with environmental pollutants can leave the skin looking worn and ravaged. Special pampering is not a matter of indulgence; it is a matter of necessity. Used regularly, the products in the Rain Forest Resources Body Care System enable all people to look their best, every day and every season.<p>


