<a name="top">
<IMG SRC="images/h_title1.jpg" ALT="Equinox International" WIDTH=483 HEIGHT=108 BORDER=0>
<center>
<font size=+2 color=#005300>Rain Forest Resources</font><BR>
<font size=+2 color=#BE8F03><i>Botanical Hair Care Products</i></font><p>
</center>




<CENTER><IMG SRC="images/p10_4.jpg" ALT="Rain Forest Hair Care" WIDTH=288 HEIGHT=158 HSPACE=10 VSPACE=10 BORDER=0></CENTER><br clear=both>

<font size=+1>Therapeutic Botanical Shampoo</font><br>
Jaboncillo Extract, Aloe Vera Gel, and Vitamin B-5 create an exceptional shampoo that gently cleans hair without damaging its delicate balance. This concentrated formula leaves the hair feeling naturally healthy, shiny, and manageable.<p>

<font size=+1>Therapeutic Botanical Conditioner</font><br>
Brazil Nut Oil moisturizes without an oily residue, and Wheat Amino Acids give fullness and body to the hair. This luxurious formula naturally nourishes the scalp and leaves hair looking shiny and silky.<p>

<font size=+1>Invigorating Hair & Scalp Treatment</font><br>
This excellent weekly treatment is ideal for hair that has been stressed by blow-drying, coloring, perms, damage from the elements like sun and wind, and pollution. Brazil Nut and Peppermint Oils penetrate deeply into the scalp, removing exfoliated particulate and stimulating hair follicles. This high performance deep conditioner helps restore luster to the hair and bring back a natural, healthy shine.<p>

<font size=+1>Botanical Styling Gel</font><br>
A unique combination of Jaboncillo Extract, Aloe Vera Gel, Matricaria Extract, and Wheat Amino Acids provides maximum styling flexibility and assures that hair is protected and moisturized while styling. This formula enables the hair to retain four times as much moisture, thus making it an excellent gel to use every day.<p>

<font size=+1>Botanical Finishing Spray</font><br>
Jaboncillo, Horsetail, and Matricaria Extracts strengthen the hair shaft and give the hair a healthy shine. This excellent finishing spray moisturizes the hair while it holds the hairstyle in place. It also delivers great last-minute styling ability.<p> 

<font size=+1>Botanical Shaving Cream</font><br>
This rich moisturizing cream softens the beard and other hair allowing for a smooth, close shave. Natural astringents leave the skin cool and refreshed; Allspice Extract imparts an exotic tropical fragrance. It is perfect for both men and women.<p>

<font size=+1>Rain Forest Resources Hair Care System</font><br>
Constantly exposed to the harsh conditions of environmental pollution, our hair is under continual assault. Even more damaging is overtreatment and long-term exposure to hair care products containing harmful chemicals. Perms, coloring, and blow-drying do not have to compromise lush, gorgeous hair. The Rain Forest Resources Hair Care System combines advanced hair care technology with nurturing botanicals from the Central and  South American rain forests. The result is a hair care system of exceptional quality that delivers the performance desired and demanded by today's consumers.<p>


For more information on how to order products or
to become an independent Equinox representative, please complete our online 
<a href="qcform.html">Inquiry Form</a>.<p>

