<h1>About Prevention:</h1>
<h2>A Web Section for Prevention Professionals
</h2>
<p>
<img src="bar3.gif"></center>
<p>
<p>
This section of the Indiana Prevention Resource Center Website is designed
to provide technical support for prevention professionals.
<p>
<h3>Prevention Reference Materials </h3>
<ul>
<li> <a href="aboutpre.html"> Articles and Publications About Prevention </a>
<li> <a href="advocacy.html"> Prevention Advocacy Resources </a>
<li> <a href=http://www.tyc.state.tx.us/prevention/40001ref.html>
 Preventon Yellow Pages </a> - Texas Youth Commission
</ul>
<p>
<p>
<h3>Prevention Materials Development Tools </h3>
<ul>
<li> <a href="photos.html"> Drug Photo Menu </a> Download pictures of drugs for 
use in your locally-produced educational materials
<li> Prevention Programming Ideas - coming soon
<li> <a href="lessons.html">Drug Education Lesson Plans </a>
</ul>
<p>
<p>
<h3>Prevention Technical Assistance</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="grants/grants.html">Grantwriting assistance</a>
</ul>                
<p>
<p>
<h3>Local Prevention Coalitions </h3>
<ul>
<li> <a href="coalition.html">Resources for Local Prevention Services Coalitions </a>
</ul>
<p>

