<font face = "arial" size = 5><b> Information about Alcohol, Tobacco, and Other Drugs </b> </font>

<ul><b>
<li><a href="/slang/home.html">On-Line Dictionary of Street Drug Slang</a>
<li><a href="/acronym/home.html">Directory of Alcohol, Tobacco and Other Drug Abbreviations and Acronyms </a>
