<h2>DRUG STATISTICS MASTER PAGE</h2>
Statistics about use and consequences of use of ALCOHOL, TOBACCO, and OTHER DRUGS<br>
from the Indiana Prevention Resource Center and other servers


<hr>
<h3>Alcohol, Tobacco, and Other Drug Use by <br>
CHILDREN AND ADOLESCENTS</h3>
<ul>

<li> <a href="/drug_stats/iprc96/home.html">
Alcohol, Tobacco, and Other Drug Use by Indiana Children and Adolescents:<br></a>
The Indiana Prevention Resource Center Survey -1996
  
<li> <a href="/drug_stats/iprc95/home.html">
Alcohol, Tobacco, and Other Drug Use by Indiana Children and Adolescents:<br></a>
The Indiana Prevention Resource Center Survey -1995


<li> <a href=http://www.isr.umich.edu/src/mtf/>
Monitoring the Future Study - 1996 </a><br>
(National High School Survey)

<li> <a href="/drug_stats/pride/home.html">
PRIDE National Drug Use Survey - Children and Adolescents - 1996<br></a>
Summary and Press Release

<li> <a href=http://www.casacolumbia.org/impact/96survey.htm> 
CASA Report: 1996 National Survey of American Attitudes on Substance 
Abuse II:  Teens and Their Parents </a>

<li> <a href=http://www.casacolumbia.org/impact/intro_gateways.htm>
CASA Report:  Cigarettes, Alcohol, Marijuana:  Gateways to Illicit 
Drug Use </a>
</ul>
<hr>

<h3>Alcohol, Tobacco, and Other Drug Use by<br>
ADULTS</h3>
<ul>
<li>Indiana Household Survey on Drug Abuse - 1994 <b>COMING SOON!</b>

<li> <a href= http://www.health.org/pubs/95hhs/ar18txt.htm>
National Household Survey on Drug Abuse - 1995 </a> <b> NCADI</b>

<li> <a href=http://www.casacolumbia.org/impact/intro_ritesofpassage.htm>
CASA Report:  Rethinking Rites of Passage:  Substance Abuse on 
America's College Campuses </a>

</ul>

<h3>CONSEQUENCES of Alcohol, Tobacco, and Other Drug Use</h3>

<ul>

<li><b>Emergency Room Statistics</b><br>
<a href= http://www.health.org/pubs/96dawn/ar17.htm>
1996 DAWN - Drug Abuse Warning Network - Advance Report No. 17 </a>

<li><b>Drug Treatment Statistics</b><br>
<a href= http://www.health.org/pubs/ndatus/ndatus.htm>
1992 NDATUS - National Drug and Alcoholism Treatment Unit Survey, 1992, and 1980-1992</a>

<li><b>Criminal Justice Statistics</b><br>
<a href= http://www.ncjrs.org>
National Criminal Justice Reference Service</a><br>
<a href= http://www2.medaccess.com/census/c_05.htm>
Criminal Justice Statistics from Statistical Abstract of the U.S. </a><br>
<a href=http://www.ojp.usdoj.gov/bjs/>
Bureau of Justice Statistics (U.S. Dept. of Justice </a> <br>
<a href=http://www.ch.search.org>
National Clearinghouse for Justice Information and Statistics </a>



<li><b>Health and Morbidity Statistics</b><br>
<ul>
<li><a href= http://www.cdc.gov/nchswww/nchshome.htm>
National Center for Health Statistics</a>

<li><a href= http://wonder.cdc.gov/>
