<li><a href= http://www.cdc.gov/epo/mmwr/mmwr.html>
Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report </a> full-text/searchable

<li> <a href=http://govinfo.kerr.orst.edu/usaco-stateis.html> 
Government Information Sharing Project </a> <br>
extensive census and government statistical data files

</ul>
</ul>

