             The Indiana Prevention Resource Center phones are
TDD-capable (telecommunications device for the deaf).  Hearing
impaired patrons should please ask to be transferred to the TDD or
request assistance in connecting with our TDD from the relay
operator.<p>
        
<a name="access">
<b>Special Access:</b></a><p>


Se habla Espa&ntilde;ol.<p>
        
