<h2>INFORMATION ABOUT ALCOHOL 
<!img src="/graphics/updated.gif">
</h2>

<p>
       

<h3>Alcohol-Related Topics</h3>
 Note:  Links to commercial sites do not imply an endorsement of products or contents.       
<ul>
<li> <a href="/publications/ncadi/alerts/home.html">Alcohol Alerts</a>
  
<li> <a href=http://www.arf.org:80/isd/pim/alcohol.html>Facts About Alcohol</a> (Addiction Research Foundation)
      
<li> <a href="/publications/iprc/factline/alcdoses.html">Alcohol Doses,
Measurements, and Blood Alcohol Levels </a>(IPRC Factline)

<li> <a href=http://www.intox.com/Physiology.html>Pharmacology and Disposition
 of Alcohol in Humans </a> (link to Intoximeters, Inc.)

<li> <a href=http://www.intox.com/Drink_Wheel.html>On-Line Blood Alcohol Calculator
("The Drink Wheel") </a> (link to Intoximeters, Inc.)

<li> <a href=http://www.intox.com/>Information on Breath Test Equipment </a>
 (link to Intoximeters, Inc.)

<li> <a href= "/publications/ncadi/primer/birthdef.htm">
Alcohol-Related Birth Outcomes (NCADI)</a><br>

<li> <a href= http://www.nwrc.org/alcohol.html>
Fetal Alcohol Syndrome (NWRC)</a><br>

<li> <a href= "/publications/ncadi/primer/binge.htm">
Binge Drinking (NCADI)</a><br>

<li> <a href="/laws/alclaw.html">
Selected Indiana Alcoholic Beverage Laws</a><br>

<li> <a href= "/publications/ncadi/primer/blood.htm">
Blood Alcohol Concentration (NCADI)</a><br>

<li> <a href= "/publications/ncadi/primer/dietary.htm">
Dietary Guidelines for Alcohol Consumption (NCADI)</a><br>

<li> <a href= "/publications/iprc/factline/lowalc.html">
Very Low Potency Alcoholic Beverages</a><br>

<li> High Potency Alcoholic Beverages</a> Under Construction.

<li> <a href= http://www.discus.health.org>
Distilled Spirits Council of the United States (DISCUS) </a> <br>
distilled spirits industry trade association

<li> <a href=http://alpha.rollanet.org/library/AlClbinger.html>Alcohol and
Calorie Content of 200 Popular Beers</a>

<li> <a href=http://www.ed.gov/pubs/PreventingSubstanceAbuse/index.html>Research
and Intervention:  Preventing Substance Abuse in Higher Education </a>

<li> <a href=http://www.linkmag.com/bacchus/>The BACCHUS and GAMMA
Peer Education Network </a><br>Student Organizations for Higher Education

<li> <a href="http://smartwine.com">Smart Wine Information (Wine Industry Info.)    </a>

<li> <a href=http://www.niaaa.nih.gov/>NIAAA - National Institute on Alchol Abuse and Alcoholism </a> 

</ul>     
<hr>
       

<h3>Impaired Driving Links</h3>
<ul>

<li> <a href=http://www.gran-net.com/madd/madd.htm>MADD:  Mothers Against
Drunk Driving (National Office)</a>

<li> <a href=http://www.arf.org/isd/pim/alc_othr.html>Facts About Alcohol, Other Drugs, and Driving 
</a>(Addiction Research Foundation)


<li> <a href= "/publications/ncadi/primer/impaired.htm">
Impaired Driving (NCADI)</a><br>

<li> <a href="/publications/iprc/factline/alcdoses.html">Alcohol Doses,
Measurements, and Blood Alcohol Levels </a>(IPRC Factline)

<li> <a href=http://www.intox.com/Physiology.html>Pharmacology and Disposition
 of Alcohol in Humans </a> (link to Intoximeters, Inc.)

<li> <a href=http://www.intox.com/Drink_Wheel.html>On-Line Blood Alcohol Calculator
("The Drink Wheel") </a> (link to Intoximeters, Inc.)

<li> <a href=http://www.intox.com/>Information on Breath Test Equipment </a>
(link to Intoximeters, Inc.)

<li> <a href=http://www.ntlgradd.netcom.com/>National GRADD: 
National Group Rides and Designated Drivers </a>

<li> <a href=http://www.3dmonth.org>National Drunk & Drugged 
Driving Prevention Menth </a>

<li> <a href=http://losangeles.digitalcity.com/RADD/>RADD:
Recording Artists, Actors, and Athletes Against Drunk Driving </a>


<li> <a href=http://ctr.usf.edu/sg/sober/sr-page.htm>Sober-Ride (Univ. of South
Florida) Designated Driver Program </a>

<li> <a href= http://www.dot.gov/affairs/sadd.htm>
SADD Contract for Life - NTHSA Praises</a><br>

<li> <a href= http://wacky.ccit.arizona.edu/~susd/dvsadd.html>
Desert View High School SADD Chapter, Tucson, Arizona</a><br>
     chapter profile, instructions for mock drunk driving crash demo

</ul>
