<li> <a href=http://www.mediapulse.com/wfs/>
Women for Sobriety, Inc.</a>

<li> <a href=http://www.med.upenn.edu/recovery/>Internet Alcohol Recovery Center (Univ. of Penn.)</a>

</ul>
       
