</ul>
       


<h3>Alcohol, Other Drugs, Sexual Behavior and AIDS</h3>

<UL><LI><A HREF = http://www.cdcnac.org>
CDC National AIDS Clearinghouse Web Server </a>

<LI><A HREF = "/publications/ncadi/radar/misc/gethigh.html">
How Getting High Can Get You AIDS</A>  -- a pamphlet from NIDA.<LI><A HREF = "/pubs/radar/misc/party.html">
How Not To Get High, Get Stupid, Get AIDS</A>  -- a guide to partying from NIDA.<LI><A HREF = "/publications/ncadi/radar/misc/alcrisk.html">
Alcohol and High Risk Sexual Behavior</A>  -- a special report to the U.S. Congress on Alcohol and Health.<LI><A HREF = "/publications/ncadi/radar/misc/sexlink.html">
Making the Link:  Sex Under the Influence of Alcohol and Other Drugs</A>  -- facts and statistics about this link.<LI><A HREF = "/publications/ncadi/radar/misc/sexual.html">
Alcohol, Disinhibition, Sexual Arousal, and Deviant Sexual Behavior</A>  -- a journal article from NIAAA's <EM>Alcohol, Health, and Research World</EM>.<LI><A HREF = "/publications/ncadi/alerts/alert15.html">
Alcohol Alert</A>  -- an article from NIAAA on alcohol and AIDS.
</ul>
