                                        7th Grade                                    8th Grade
                        ----------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------
                                          State                                     State                 Natnl
                        ----------------------------------------- --------------------------------------- ------
                        1991   1992   1993   1994   1995   1996   1991   1992  1993   1994   1995   1996   1995
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Cigarettes           31.7   31.5   28.4   29.7   29.8   31.4*  39.1   41.8   37.9   39.6   41.4   42.6     NA

    Smokeless Tobacco    14.4   13.2   10.9   11.7   11.9   10.2   20.1   22.8   14.9   16.5   15.4   14.2*    NA

