    Psychedelics          3.7    5.7    4.5    4.1    7.6    6.4    4.2    5.6    4.5    4.4    8.2    6.0*   4.0

    Heroin                1.2    1.4    -.-    -.-    -.-    -.-    -.-    1.8    -.-    -.-    -.-    1.1   -.-

    Steroids              1.6    1.9    -.-    1.1    1.0    -.-    1.2    2.1    -.-    -.-    -.-    -.-   -.-
    -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NOTES: NA - Indicates that data were not available
       	Natl - Data from the National High School Survey, 1995
       	-.-  - denotes values less than 1.0%
        		* - denotes that the 1995 and 1996 percentages are significantly different using a 5% significance level 

