<h2>ALCOHOL, TOBACCO, AND OTHER DRUG USE<br>
BY INDIANA CHILDREN AND ADOLESCENTS</h2>
<h3>The Indiana Prevention Resource Center Survey - 1995<br>
Prevalence Statistics - <i>Main Findings</i></h3>
<p>
<hr size=10>
<p>
