<h2>Indiana Together:  Strategies for achieiving a drug-free Indiana</h2>
<h3>Problem Indicators Table #1</h3>
<hr>
<p>
<b>1. Deaths caused by alcohol- or other drug-related motor vehicle crashes.

1991 -- 318 deaths<br>
1992 -- 262 deaths<br>
1993 -- 228 deaths<br>
