     technical consultants for ATOD non-profits

<li> <a href= http://www.lec.org>
Life Education Network</a><br>

<li> <a href= http://www.odn.ohio.gov/ohio/odad/odada.htmlx>
Ohio Dept. of Alcohol and Drug Addiction Services </a>

