<html>
<head>
<title>IPRC Indiana Resources Database</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor = "#ffffff">
<!-- header start -->
<!-- header end -->

<!-- title map start -->
<MAP NAME="titlemap">
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="70,68,142,83" HREF=/about/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="146,67,212,83" HREF=/prevention/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="217,67,276,83" HREF=/druginfo/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="278,67,341,83" HREF=/drug_stats/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="345,67,420,83" HREF=/publications/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="425,68,492,83" HREF=/resources/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="497,68,546,83" HREF=/prclib/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="550,67,592,83" HREF=/search/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=default HREF=/home.html>
</MAP><!-- title map end -->

<!-- title image start -->
<center>
<img border = 0 src = "/graphics/title_banner.gif" usemap = "#titlemap">
<p>
</center>
<!-- title image end -->

<center><font size=5>Local Prevention Coordination in Indiana</font></center>
<p>
<center><img src=/graphics/logos/local.jpg></center>
<p>

An Indiana Prevention Resource database of local prevention coordination
agencies in each of Indiana's 92 counties. Information includes contact
names, addresses, and telephone numbers for:<p>

<ul>
<li>Local Coordinating Councils (alcohol and other drug program coordination)
<li>Step Ahead Councils (social service agency coordination)
<li>Regional Office of the Governor's Commission for a Drug Free Indiana serving that county
<li>Safe and Drug-Free Schools Coordinators for each school corporation in the county.
</ul>

Enter the name of the county OR the name of a city or incorportated town.<p>

<form method = "post" action = "/cgi-bin/scripts/county.pl">
City <input name="city" size=48"><p>
or County <input name="county" size=48"><p>
<input type = submit value = "Start Search">
<input type = reset value = "Reset Form">
</form>

Send updates via email to: <a href="mailto:wpearson@indiana.edu"">Billie Pearson</a><p>

<p>
<hr>

<!-- footer start -->
<i><a href="http://www.drugs.indiana.edu">Indiana Prevention Resource Center</a></i>
<br>
<!-- footer end -->

