<html>
<head>
<title>Prevention PROfiles</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor = "#ffffff">
<!-- header start -->
<!-- header end -->

<!-- title map start -->
<MAP NAME="titlemap">
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="70,68,142,83" HREF=/about/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="146,67,212,83" HREF=/prevention/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="217,67,276,83" HREF=/druginfo/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="278,67,341,83" HREF=/drug_stats/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="345,67,420,83" HREF=/publications/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="425,68,492,83" HREF=/resources/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="497,68,546,83" HREF=/prclib/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="550,67,592,83" HREF=/search/home.html>
<AREA SHAPE=default HREF=/home.html>
</MAP><!-- title map end -->

<!-- title image start -->
<center>
<img border = 0 src = "/graphics/title_banner.gif" usemap = "#titlemap">
<p>
</center>
<!-- title image end -->


<table cellspacing = 5>
<tr>
<td valign = "top">
<img  src=/graphics/profiles_s.gif></center>
<td>
<tr>
<td valign = "top">
</center>
<p>
<font face = "arial" color = "blue">
The <i>Indiana Prevention Resource Center</i> Prevention PROfiles database
contains listings of nearly 2000 local prevention programs throughout
Indiana. Each PROfile includes program name, information on the sponsoring
organization, mailing address, telephone numbers and contact names, a program
abstract, and information about funding sources.<p>
</td>

<td valign = "top">

<FORM METHOD="POST" ACTION="http://129.79.74.163/scripts/dbWeb/dbwebc.dll/profiles_public?getxresults">
<b>Search Prevetion PROfiles...</b><br>
Enter the information that you would like to search for in the boxes below.
You do not need to enter something in every box. Also note that only matches
which meet all criteria will be returned. <a href="#example">Here's</a> an
example search.
<p>
<table>
<tr>
<td valign = top>
<b>County Code</b>
</td>
<td valign = top>
<input NAME="6,Profiles,ID" value = "contains" type = "hidden">
<INPUT NAME="1,Profiles,ID" VALUE="" SIZE="40" MAXLENGTH="75">
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign = top>
<b>City</b>
</td>
<td valign = top>
<input type = "hidden" NAME="6,Profiles,City" value = "contains">
<INPUT NAME="1,Profiles,City" VALUE="" SIZE="40" MAXLENGTH="75">
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign = top>
<b>Abstract</b>
</td>
<td valign = top>
<input type = "hidden" NAME="6,Profiles,Abstract" value = "contains">
<INPUT NAME="1,Profiles,Abstract" VALUE="" SIZE="40" MAXLENGTH="75">
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign = top>
</td>
<td valign = top>
<input type = "submit" value="search"><p>
<input type = "reset" value = "start over"><p>
(click <a href="linux/home.html">here</a> to search all fields)
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</center>
</form>
</table>
<a name = "example">
<b>Example Search:</b></a>
<p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>To search for all programs in the city of Clinton, Indiana, simply type
Clinton into the City box.
<li>To find all programs in the city of Clinton which
address alcohol, type Clinton in the city box and alcohol in the abstract box.

<li>To search for programs in <i>any</i> city which address
alcohol, type alcohol into the abstract box but leave the city box
blank.

</ul>
</blockquote>


</center>
