Alcohol and Other Drug Use by Children and Adolescents:  Evidence of the
'Gateway Drug Effect."  <i>Journal of School Health</i> 63:302-306, 
September, 1993.
<p>
Johnston LD, O'Malley PM, Bachman JG.  <i>National Trends in Drug Use and
Related Factors among American High School Students and Young Adults, 1975-1986.</i>
Washington, DC:  National Institute on Drug Abuse, U.S. Dept. of Health and
Human Services publication (ADM) 87-1535, pp. 248-255, 1987.
<p>
