<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff><center>
<img src="title_ba.gif">
<h1>Photos of Drugs</h1>
<h2>from the U.S. Drug Enforcement Administration </h2>
<p>
<p>
<img src="bar3.gif"></center>
<p>
<p>
This menu will allow prevention professionals to access color photographs 
of drugs and drug-related topics that can be downloaded and used in 
locally-produced prevention materials, such as overhead transparencies, 
slides, posters, and handout materials.
<p>
Users of Netscape can download a graphic by simply touching the graphic
with their cursor, and then "clicking" on the right hand mouse button, 
which will reveal a graphics menu.  Just select "save this image" and
then follow the instructions.  Users of other browser software should
consult the documentation for their browser for downloading instructions 
if using the right hand mouse button does not work.
<p>
All of the photos linked below appear to be in the public domain, and are 
presented in menus that imply permission to download.  To be sure that 
no copyright laws are violated, we recommend securing the permission of 
the Website before using any graphic beyond the "fair educational use" 
allowed by the federal copyright laws.
<p>

<p>
<p>
Photos from <b><i>Drugs of Abuse</b></i>
<p>
<ul>

<li> <a href=http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/abuse/chap7/photo/photo.htm>
Anabolic Steroids Photos </a> gif photo files of anabolic steroids

<li> <a href=http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/abuse/chap3/depress/photo/photo.htm>
Depressants Photos </a> gif photo files of depressant drugs

<li> <a href=http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/abuse/chap5/photo/photo.htm>
Hallucinogens Photos </a> gif photo files of hallucinogenic drugs

<li> <a href=http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/abuse/chap6/photo/photo.htm>
Marijuana/Cannabis Photos </a> gif photo files of marijuana & cannabis

<li> <a href=http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/abuse/chap1/photo/photo.htm>
Miscellaneous Drug-Related Photos </a> gif photo files of miscellaneous drugs,
including additional photos of narcotics, cocaine, marijuana, etc.

<li> <a href=http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/abuse/chap2/narcotic/photo/photo.htm>
Narcotics Photos </a> gif photo files of narcotic drugs

<li> <a href=http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/abuse/chap4/stimula/photo/photo.htm>
Stimulants Photos </a> gif photo files of stimulant drugs

</ul>
<p>
<p>
