<TITLE>Indiana PRC - Prevention Support - NCADI Drug Photo Menu  </TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
 <center><h1>Drug Photos from the NCADI Website </h1><p>
<img src="bar3.gif"></center><p>
<p>This menu will allow prevention professionals to access color 
photographs of drugs and drug-related topics that can be downloaded and 
used in locally-produced prevention materials, such as overhead 
transparencies, slides, posters, and handout materials.<p>
Users of Netscape can download a graphic by simply touching the 
graphic with their cursor, and then "clicking" on the right hand mouse 
button, which will reveal a graphics menu.  Just select "save this 
graphic" and then follow the instructions.  Users of other browser 
software should consult the documentation for their browser for 
downloading instructions if using the right hand mouse button does not 
work.<p>
All of the photos linked below are in the the public domain.<p>
<ul><li> <a href="/graphics/photographs/ncadi/alcohol.gif">
Alcohol</a>
<li> <a href="/graphics/photographs/ncadi/aod.gif">
Alcohol and Other Drugs</a>
