Alcohol, Tobacoo and Other Drugs</a>
<li> <a href="/graphics/photographs/ncadi/drugs.gif">
Other Drugs</a>
<li> <a href="/graphics/photographs/ncadi/smoker.gif">
Person lighting cigarette</a> 

