<HTML><HEAD><title>Indiana PRC - Prevention Support - Drug Education Lesson Ideas</title></HEAD><BODY bgcolor = "#ffffff"><!-- header start --><!-- header end --><!-- title map start --><MAP NAME="titlemap"><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="70,68,142,83" HREF=/about/home.html><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="146,67,212,83" HREF=/prevention/home.html><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="217,67,276,83" HREF=/druginfo/home.html><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="278,67,341,83" HREF=/drug_stats/home.html><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="345,67,420,83" HREF=/publications/home.html><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="425,68,492,83" HREF=/resources/home.html><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="497,68,546,83" HREF=/prclib/home.html><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="550,67,592,83" HREF=/search/home.html><AREA SHAPE=default HREF=/home.html></MAP><!-- title map end --><!-- title image start --><center><img border = 0 src = "/graphics/title_banner.gif" usemap = "#titlemap"><p></center><!-- title image end --><center><h1>DRUG EDUCATION LESSON IDEAS:<br>
Countering the Influence of Alcohol and Tobacco Advertising</h1>
<img src="bar3.gif"></center><p><center>
<h3>This section is under construction -- watch for frequent 
updates!</h3></center><p>
<p><h2>Ideas for Classroom or After-School Prevention Activities 
</h2><p>

<h3>General Advertising Literacy Links </h3>
<ul>
<li> <a href=http://www.adbusters.org/adbusters/main.html>
Adbusters </a> homepage for Adbusters Magazine
<li> <a href=http://websites.earthlink.net/~cml/cml.html>
Center for Media Literacy  </a>
<li> <a href=http://interact.uoregon.edu/medialit/homepage>
Media Literacy Online Project </a>
</ul>
<p>
<h3>Countering Tobacco Advertising Links </h3>
<ul><li> <a href=http://world.std.com/~batteryb/>
The BADvertising Institute </a> debunking tobacco ads through humor
<li> <a href=http://www.kickbutt.org>
Kickbutt.org Homepage </a> Washington DOC -Doctor's Ought to Care 
medical advocacy organization
<li> <a href=http://www.boutell.com/infact/>
INFACT's Tobacco Industry Campaign </a>
<li> <a href=http://www.rwjf.org/media/tobacco.htm>
Media Resource Guide on Tobacco </a> - Robert Wood Johnson Foundation
<li> <a href=http://sailor.lib.md.us/topics/tobacco.txt>
No Sale:  Youth, Tobacco, and Responsible Retailing </a>
<li> <a href=http://www.health.org/kidsarea/pubs/sgr4kids/adbust.htm>
Be An Ad-Buster </a> Surgeon General's Report for Kids
<li> <a href=http://www.os.dhhs.gov/epsa/nsmk/contents.html>
Smoke-Free Kids </a> Office on Smoking and Health
</ul><p>

<h3>Countering Alcohol Advertising Links </h3>
<ul>
<li><a href=http://www.pcvp.org/alcohol/alctab4.html>
Hands Off Halloween Campaign </a> media campaign to remove alcohol ads
linked to Halloween
<li><a href=http://www.earthisland.org/uhp/r11-billb.html>
"Alcohol & Tobacco Billboards Target Communities of Color"</a>
<li><a href=http://www.arlington.net/news/doc/1047/1:FRONT2/1:FRONT2090296.html>
"MADD Targets Bud Frogs, Underage Drinking"</a>
<li> <a href=http://www.health.org/kidsarea/pubs/ver/seeing.htm>
Is Seeing Believing? </a> NCADI
</ul>
<p>

