<p>
(36) Trocki, K. F., & Leigh, B. C.  Alcohol consumption and unsafe sex:  
A comparison of heterosexuals and homosexual men.  Journal of Acquired Immune 
Deficiency Syndromes 4(10):981-986, 1991.
