<DOCNO>WT05-B06-175</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA014-000151-B042-306</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://prc-wwwserv.idap.indiana.edu:80/pubs/radar/keeping/feel.html 129.79.74.155 19970217115154 text/html 14124
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 17 Feb 1997 12:04:11 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.3
