<h2>Indiana Together:  Strategies for achieiving a drug-free Indiana</h2>
<h3>Problem Indicators Table #2</h3>
<hr>
<p>
<b>2. Single vehicle nighttime accidents.

1991 -- 4580 accidents<br>
1992 -- 4467 accidents<br>
1993 -- 4422 accidents<br>
<p>

County Summary<br>
Decreases 1993 -- 38 counties<br>
Increases 1993 -- 32 counties<br>
No Change -- 22 counties<br>
<p>
<center>
