<TITLE>Indiana-Alcohol/Drug-related Birth Effects Stats -- Indiana PRC</TITLE>

<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
<h2>Indiana Together:  Strategies for achieiving a drug-free Indiana</h2>
<h3>Problem Indicators Table #12</h3>
<hr>
<p>
<b>12.  Incidence of alcohol- and other drug-related negative birth outcomes.</b>
<p>
<p>
Low Birth Weight Per 1,000 Live Births
<p>
1989 - 66.5 <br>
1990 - 66.0 <br>
1991 - 67.3 <br>
1992 - 68.4 <br>
<p>
Lag time in reporting data precludes showing 1993 data.  In 1992, nine Indiana
counties reported incidence of Fetal Alcohol Syndrome.  Most counties do not
track this data.
<center>
