<h2>Indiana Together:  Strategies for achieiving a drug-free Indiana</h2>
<h3>Problem Indicators Table #3</h3>
<hr>
<p>
<b>3. Deaths caused by cirrhosis.

1990 -- 419 deaths<br>
7.55 per 100,000 population
<p>
1991 -- 425 deaths<br>
7.58 per 100,000 population
<p>

<p>
