<HTML>
<TITLE>Indiana-Per Capita Alcohol Consumption Stats -- Indiana PRC</TITLE>

<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
<h2>Indiana Together:  Strategies for achieiving a drug-free Indiana</h2>
<h3>Problem Indicators Table #10</h3>
<hr>
<p>
<b>10. Average per-capita consumption of alcohol.</b>
<p>
Figures show gallons of actual ethanol alcohol consumed per-capita.  Indiana
ranked in the 3rd decile nationally for amounts consumed.
<p>
<p>
<table border=3>
<tr><th>  </th><th>1980</th><th>1991</th></tr>
<tr><td>All Beverages</td><td>2.11</td><td>2.01</td></tr>
<tr><td>Beer</td><td>1.27</td><td>1.22</td></tr>
<tr><td>Wine</td><td>.20</td><td>.19</td></tr>
<tr><td>Spirits</td><td>.64</td><td>.60</td><tr>
</table>
<p>
