Readability:  Easy<BR>
Availability:  Channing L. Bete Co., Inc., 200 State Road, South Deerfield, MA 01373, 800-628-7733
<BLOCKQUOTE>This booklet tells a short story about two adult gay men.  One of the men develops the symptoms of AIDS.  It is revealed that he used to shoot drugs and have unprotected sex.  Steps to prevent AIDS transmission and infection are described.  An explanation of how to clean needles is included.</BLOCKQUOTE>
