<BLOCKQUOTE>This fact sheet provides sobering facts about alcoholism, including statistics on consumption rates, alcohol and accidents, and alcoholism among special populations.  It also provides information on treatment and offers recommendations regarding public policy.  </BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<B>Sober Skipper</B><BR>
Year:  1992<BR>
